comments: Favors (NOP) jumps A to B into the body of Butler (MIA) and the contact affects his shot attempt at the basket.
Williamson (NOP) establishes himself in a legal screening position in the path of Hill (MIA) and does not deliver contact.
Favors (NOP) is drawn in the air towards Robinson (MIA) and he makes contact to the body that affects his ability to pass.
Adebayo (MIA) makes contact to the body of Ingram (NOP) that affects his SQBR.
Butler (MIA) makes incidental "high-five" contact with Ingram (NOP) after the release that does not affect his jump shot attempt.
Adebayo (MIA) firms up in a in a screening position in the path of Ball (NOP).
Favors (NOP) maintains a legal guarding position during the driving shot attempt by Adebayo (MIA).
Jones Jr. (MIA) commits a take foul on Ball (NOP).
Hill (MIA) makes clean contact with the ball when he dislodges it from Melli (NOP).
Melli (NOP) makes contact to the arm of Hill (MIA) that affects his ability to secure the ball.
Adebayo (MIA) commits a take foul on Holiday (NOP).
Butler (MIA) commits a take foul on Hart (NOP).
